# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DEPENDENCY NOTES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# RIVERPOD: State management
# - flutter_riverpod: Main package
# - riverpod_annotation: Code generation annotations
# - riverpod_generator: Code generation (dev)
# 
# FIREBASE: Backend
# - firebase_core: Required for all Firebase packages
# - firebase_auth: SMS authentication
# - cloud_firestore: Database
# - cloud_functions: Server-side validation
# - firebase_crashlytics: Error reporting
# - firebase_analytics: Usage tracking
# - firebase_performance: Performance monitoring
# 
# HIVE: Offline storage
# - Used for caching cases locally
# - Reduces Firestore reads
# 
# DARTZ: Functional programming
# - Either type for error handling
# - Clean Architecture pattern
# 
# EQUATABLE: Value equality
# - Required for entities
# - Simplifies testing
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
